Pixivloader
===========
A simple tool for downloading tags/search results from Pixiv. 
Filtering results based on user favorites is possible.

1. Dependencies
===============
Pixivloader requires Python (>=2.6) to operate.

The following additional Python modules are required:
* mechanize
* lxml

2. Installation
===============
No installation is required. pixivloader.py is the main executable.

3. Usage
========
pixivloader.py --help for a list of possible options.
One of -t, -s or -g is required to specify either:

-t	Image tag
-s	Search string
-g	Member ID


